        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p><add>Hebrew</add></p>
			<p><placeName>Barnet St No 26</placeName>.</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p><add>Hebrew</add></p>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>&#44; <date>Thursday&#44; Fast of Esther&#44;<lb/>1852</date></p>
			<p>To my dear friend&#44; etc.&#44; <sic><addressee>Rabbi Isaac Elazar</addressee></sic>&#58;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Yesterday I received your delightful letter and I am sorry that<lb/> I am unable to do your wish. For&#44; all my days in this land I refrained<lb/> from giving a &#34;Get&#34;. This winter <persName>Dr. Adler</persName>&#44; the Rabbi of <placeName>London</placeName> and also<lb/> his son&#45;in&#45;law&#44; the Rabbi of <placeName>Hamburg</placeName>&#44; wrote to me about the matter of a<lb/> certain &#34;Get&#34; in <placeName>New York</placeName>. And there&#44; too&#44; I did not grant their request.<lb/> My point of view and my principle are not to give a &#34;Get&#34;&#44; especially at<lb/> this time&#44; since in <placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; in the Beth Midrash&#44; there are many scholars<lb/> who want to do such things.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">And now&#44; my dear friend&#44; because of the crisis in the country&#44; I<lb/> have been forced to give up my business now about 6 months&#44; and I have<lb/> been sitting at home as in my first days. I beg of you to send me through<lb/> Adam&#39;s express&#44; the &#34;Jeshurun&#34; of <persName>Dr. Hirsch</persName> for the years<lb/> consisting of volume 59&#44; 60&#44; and 61. I shall return it to you as soon as<lb/> possible. If you can do so&#44; it will be a great favor to me. For the<lb/> past 2 months I have not received the &#34;Occident&#34;. I don&#39;t know why. Perhaps<lb/> because I left home.</p>
          <p rend="indent(8)">Your faithful friend&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">Abraham Rice</persName></p>
          <p rend="indent(10)"><placeName>Barnet Street # 26</placeName>.</p>
          
        </body>
